</td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> So you've always wanted to lead a dragon raid...</span><hr size=1> After some long and hard thought, I've decided that the next Nagafen raid will be the last Dragon raid I lead for the KCoG.  I've participated in, helped admin, or led something like 9 raids against Naggy now (and more than that against Vox).  I hit level 49 almost a year ago, and I've still only 52 now...<br>
<br>
So regardless of whether or not Naggy coughs up a book for me on the next raid, I'm gonna level into 53 and beyond and start seeing a little more of the world of Norrath.  As much as I'd like to have my Fiery Avenger, it's time to move on.<br>
<br>
Now, there will probably be at least one (if not half-a-freakin' dozen) Vox raids before then, and the next Naggy raid will most likely end up sometime in November or something... but I figured I'd get a head-start on this now rather than wait any longer.<br>
<br>
So, the real point of this post is that I'm now looking for a guild (preferably a guild rather than a single person) who would be interested in taking over my role as the KCoG Dragon raid leader.  I can't really consider leading a raid that I can't participate in... I have a hard time asking people to bleed and die when I'm not fighting beside them or leading the charge.  (Note: I expect Talovar and myself will most likely be leading the Severilous raid, whenever that happens).<br>
<br>
If you or your guild are interested, feel free to contact me in game - if I'm not on as Kommisar, I may be playing my bard, Defttone (with 2 T's).  You can also drop me an email:<br>
anubis@chrometiger.com<br>
<br>
If your wondering what it takes to lead a raid... Kellory had a great post about it on a thread a while back... I'll see if I can find it and bump it in the near future.<br>
<br>
It's been a great pleasure leading KCoG raids, and I'm sure I'll miss doing it.  I only hope I can teach someone to take up the reigns as well as Haemish and Lagdalen taught me. <p>-Kommisar Nils "Can-Head" Hansen -- Guild Officer. Master Smith. Tank.
KCoG Dragon Liason
